---
const photo = 'https://images.pexels.com/photos/33744867/pexels-photo-33744867.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1400';
---
<section class="built section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="built__grid">
      <div class="built__media">
        <img src={photo} alt="Family enjoying time together" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="built__badge">
          <span class="built__badge-icon">❤️</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Built by parents</strong>
            <span class="muted">For parents</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="built__copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why we made this</span>
        <h2 class="mt-4">Because we got tired of Googling, too.</h2>
        <p class="lede mt-4">
          FamPass started in a kitchen in Orange County. Two parents, three
          kids between them, and one shared frustration: there was no good way
          to find out what was happening for kids each week.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          City rec centers had PDFs from 2019. Library calendars hid in the
          fifth tab of a sub-page. Mom group threads were great until you
          tried to search them. We wanted one app that pulled it all together —
          honestly and without the marketing fluff.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          That's what FamPass is. We're parents shipping a tool we wished
          existed. We use it ourselves every Saturday morning.
        </p>

        <ul class="built__values">
          <li>
            <span class="built__values-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔒</span>
            <div>
              <strong>No data resold.</strong>
              <span>We don't sell your location, your kids' ages, or anything else.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="built__values-icon" aria-hidden="true">🤝</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Honest sourcing.</strong>
              <span>Every event credits its source. We don't pretend to know what we don't.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="built__values-icon" aria-hidden="true">🧭</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Locally curated.</strong>
              <span>A real human reviews flagged events. Our sourcing gets a weekly check-in.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .built__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.05fr;
    gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .built__media {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: visible;
  }
  .built__media img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 5 / 6;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .built__badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 24px;
    left: 24px;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    padding: 12px 18px 12px 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .built__badge-icon {
    width: 38px; height: 38px;
    background: var(--color-accent-lo);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .built__badge strong { display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-ink); }
  .built__badge .muted { font-size: 0.82rem; }

  .built__copy h2 { max-width: 480px; }
  .built__copy .lede { max-width: 540px; }
  .built__copy p { max-width: 540px; }

  .built__values {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    padding-top: 28px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    max-width: 540px;
  }
  .built__values li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .built__values-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    background: var(--color-bg-warm);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 18px;
  }
  .built__values strong {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .built__values span:not(.built__values-icon) {
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .built__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .built__media { max-width: 480px; margin-inline: auto; }
  }
</style>
